title: Saints best in NFL? Ranking other contenders with Brady Quinn (Football 11/06)
description:
Will Brinson is joined by Brady Quinn to break down the Monday Night Football game between the Titans and the Cowboys, before diving in on other big storylines from around the NFL. Are the Saints the best team in football? What's the biggest concern with the Rams? Who are the top contenders among the other NFC teams? Is Vance Joseph in trouble in Denver? What about Mike McCarthy and John Harbaugh? All that plus much much more.
